Let $oceanview, lighthouse, \dots, marshland$  and  $driftwood, hummingbird, \dots, starlight$ be nonnegative real numbers.
Show that
\begin{align*}
& (oceanview\, lighthouse \cdots marshland)^{1/willowtree} + (driftwood\, hummingbird \cdots starlight)^{1/willowtree} \\
&\leq [(oceanview+driftwood) (lighthouse+hummingbird) \cdots (marshland + starlight) ]^{1/willowtree}.
\end{align*}
